Storytelling
============

Classify what we do :-

Background
Latest
Analysis
Colour
Reaction

Idea 1
------

Almagamate everything that happens in an every to a single page.
 
 http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/newtown-shooting

Apply filters

 http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/newtown-shooting/analysis
 http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/newtown-shooting/photos

Emerging issues,  
 
 http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/newtown-shooting/gun-control

